sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Client
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant MCAD as MCAD Controller<br/>In-Process
    participant InstaScale as InstaScale Controller<br/>In-Process
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant MachineAPI as OpenShift Machine API
    participant CloudAPI as Cloud Provider API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraper

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: AppWrapper Submission and Scheduling
    User->>K8sAPI: Create AppWrapper CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    K8sAPI-->>MCAD: Watch event (in-memory)<br/>AppWrapper created
    MCAD->>K8sAPI: Queue AppWrapper<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    MCAD->>K8sAPI: Update AppWrapper status: Queued<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
    MCAD->>K8sAPI: Check resource availability<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    MCAD->>K8sAPI: Create Pods/Services<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    MCAD->>K8sAPI: Update AppWrapper status: Running<br/>HTTPS/6443

    Note over InstaScale,CloudAPI: Flow 2: InstaScale Node Scaling (Optional, OpenShift)
    InstaScale->>K8sAPI: Watch AppWrappers<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>InstaScale: AppWrapper event: Pending resources
    InstaScale->>K8sAPI: Read cluster nodes<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
    InstaScale->>MachineAPI: Create MachineSet<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    MachineAPI->>CloudAPI: Provision VM instances<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: Cloud credentials
    CloudAPI-->>MachineAPI: New nodes provisioned
    MachineAPI-->>K8sAPI: Nodes join cluster

    Note over MCAD,KubeRay: Flow 3: MCAD RayCluster Management
    MCAD->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>KubeRay: Watch event: RayCluster created
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Create Ray Head/Worker Pods<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    KubeRay->>K8sAPI: Update RayCluster status<br/>HTTPS/6443
    K8sAPI-->>MCAD: Watch event: RayCluster Running
    MCAD->>K8sAPI: Update AppWrapper status: Completed<br/>HTTPS/6443

    Note over Prometheus,MCAD: Flow 4: Prometheus Metrics Scraping
    Prometheus->>MCAD: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    MCAD-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics<br/>HTTP response
